key "KG11"

\end_inset

, as well as the linear programming approach of 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "Kol15"

\end_inset

 unsuitable for the analysis of my model.
 I approach it by representing signaling structures as a certain class of
 convex functions and then using calculus of variations to find the first-order
 necessary conditions.
 
